title: H & T Seafood, Inc. Recalls Siluriformes Products Produced without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, Jan. 18, 2019 H & T Seafood, Inc., the Importer of Record, a Bell, Calif. firm, is recalling approximately 71,435 pounds of imported Siluriformes fish products because the products were not presented for import re-inspection upon entry into the United States, the U.S. Department...
